{"tid":1692462,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［重組記者］大家可唔可以畀多次機會前線記者","createTime":"2019-11-04T05:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T17:09:25.000Z","uid":174174,"like":9,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"53347b202c5335ce6c4123b3504e0792b70ace2b","tid":1692462,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:44:47.000Z","msg":"利申：絕對支持打爛器材，噴黑鏡頭/記者，綁住佢哋，甚或升級至召喚神獸<br />\n<br />\n不過有個策略想睇吓咁多位手足認唔認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係用文宣表示<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">以兩個星期為限期</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港傳媒已死，豈至tvb?</span></span><br />\n仲有香港01，新華社，星島日報，東方日報，文匯報，大公報，南華早報，巴士的報，am730...打都打唔哂<br />\n<br />\n2.  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">民眾對黨媒嘅仇恨值未夠</span></span><br />\n加上可以加強我哋用武力嘅合法性，雖然咁多位手足可能已死心，覺得要走一早走咗，但起碼可以同人講，「警告同機會就畀咗，要錢有錢要工有工，咁都唔辭職就係你哋自己親手埋葬香港第四權」<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">黃色經濟圈</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我哋要<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">配合文宣同勇武行動</span>，和勇一齊合作煲大呢條戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nStep 1. <ins><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">發起眾籌，加入黃媒，實踐公義<br />\n</span></span></ins><br />\n主要目的：整一筆錢去吸納跳槽嘅前線記者<br />\n<br />\n- 香城教育電視眾籌計劃 HKGETV Crowdfunding Campaign<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1676052\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1676052</a><br />\n<br />\n- 各大專院校嘅編委會<br />\n<br />\n- 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://mystand.thestandnews.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfhSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=6dd76f7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmystand.thestandnews.com&h=406cb5b9\" target=\"_blank\">https://mystand.thestandnews.com</a><br />\n<br />\nStep 2. <ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">武力不斷升級係我哋最大嘅籌碼</span></ins><br />\n針對建築物、拍攝儀器 &mdash;＞ 起底 &mdash;＞搞記者證/隨身物品&mdash;＞搞記者 （流血嘅話要幫手諗有力理據，咪一味叫唔好）<br />\n當然都睇實際情況 佢反抗咪直接升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nStep 3. <ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">總結成績表</span></ins><br />\n記者跳槽，對成場運動可以好大影響同啟示<br />\n慢慢順延到黨鐵...中資公司員工...政府部門<br />\n將整個極權體制解體，亦唔再存在「仲有好人論」！"},{"pid":"3ee642ce9610fa0c27c2e1de328333b8a76f4a24","tid":1692462,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">解散黨媒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f84049be6ab9087ef2ed281fff07efdb263330a","tid":1692462,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3115cae55454e3368fb0441b16bcca69a59bd19e","tid":1692462,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"2星期太耐<br />\n區議會之前一定唔好比TVB報到新聞<br />\n今晚我要見到各大屋苑要有人不停loop CCTvb 惡行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692177</a>"},{"pid":"a535232af15cc74dc713904d504953c3e387a164","tid":1692462,"uid":156341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"左膠死全家"},{"pid":"493b5c3dbe79669c21e4e1f6360628bb509cda6f","tid":1692462,"uid":174174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3115cae55454e3368fb0441b16bcca69a59bd19e","tid":1692462,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T05:50:49.000Z","msg":"2星期太耐<br />\n區議會之前一定唔好比TVB報到新聞<br />\n今晚我要見到各大屋苑要有人不停loop CCTvb 惡行<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692177\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692177</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"巴打覺得應該幾耐？<br />\n我純粹考慮有足夠時間去行動升級<br />\n同埋辭職都要啲時間<img src=\"